{
  "style": "IEEE",
  "texts": [
    "The ViT encoder captures long-range dependencies and global spatial patterns through self-attention, while the CNN decoder upsamples these representations to generate the final segmentation mask.",
    "The model is implemented using the self-attention-cv library, 3 which offers a configurable framework for UNETR architectures.",
    "We set the number of ViT attention heads and base filters to M = 2P, matching the copra configuration.",
    "The transformer encoder employs the GELU activation function [63], while all convolutional and transposed-convolutional layers in the decoder use ReLU.",
    "As in copra, each convolutional layer is followed by two Instance Normalization layers."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
    "The transformer encoder employs the GELU activation function [63], while all convolutional and transposed-convolutional layers in the decoder use ReLU."
  ]
}